WEBVTT

00:08:58.820 --> 00:09:02.664
to intentionally seek out
those closest to the trauma

00:09:02.688 --> 00:09:04.425
and check in with them.

00:09:06.069 --> 00:09:08.617
Many schools are doing what they can

00:09:08.641 --> 00:09:10.308
to fill in the gaps,

00:09:10.332 --> 00:09:12.856
starting with acknowledging
that the work that we do

00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:14.499
is downright hard.

00:09:15.768 --> 00:09:18.098
Another school in Lincoln,
Schoo Middle School,

00:09:18.122 --> 00:09:20.433
has what they call "Wellness Wednesdays."

00:09:21.006 --> 00:09:23.482
They invite in community yoga teachers,

00:09:23.506 --> 00:09:26.799
they sponsor walks around
the neighborhood during lunch

00:09:26.823 --> 00:09:28.230
and organize social events

00:09:28.254 --> 00:09:30.952
that are all meant
to bring people together.